<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>IT Security Compliance Notice</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: auto; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 4px; }
    .header { background: #c0392b; color: #fff; padding: 16px 24px; }
    .header h2 { margin: 0; font-size: 18px; }
    .body { padding: 24px; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; }
    .cta { display: inline-block; margin: 16px 0; padding: 12px 24px;
           background: #c0392b; color: #fff; text-decoration: none;
           border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; }
    .footer { background: #f4f4f4; padding: 12px 24px; font-size: 12px; color: #888;
              border-top: 1px solid #ddd; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="header">
    <h2>&#9888; URGENT: IT Security Compliance Action Required</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="body">
    <!-- GoPhish template variables use {{.Variable}} Go-template syntax -->
    <p>Dear {% raw %}{{.FirstName}}{% endraw %},</p>
    <p>Our automated security compliance system has flagged your account for
    <strong>immediate verification</strong>. Failure to complete this process
    within <strong>24 hours</strong> will result in temporary account suspension
    in accordance with policy SEC-2024-11.</p>
    <p>Issues detected:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Unreviewed security policy acknowledgement (overdue 7 days)</li>
      <li>Multi-factor authentication status: pending re-verification</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Please click the button below to verify your compliance status:</p>
    <a href="{% raw %}{{.URL}}{% endraw %}" class="cta">Verify Compliance Now</a>
    <p>If you believe this message was sent in error, contact the IT Security
    helpdesk at <em>security@company.internal</em> and quote reference
    <strong>SEC-{% raw %}{{.RId}}{% endraw %}</strong>.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    This message was sent by the IT Security Compliance System on behalf of
    {% raw %}{{.From}}{% endraw %}. Do not reply to this email.
    <!-- GoPhish tracking pixel -->
    {% raw %}<img src="{{.TrackingURL}}" alt="" width="1" height="1"/>{% endraw %}
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
